When it comes to natural deodorant, one size doesn’t fit all. 

That’s why Woohoo offers a range of different deodorant strengths. Because whether you sweat like a champion or have skin that reacts to just about everything, the right formula can make allllll the difference.

But what actually is deodorant strength? And how do you know which one is right for you? Let’s break it down ☝️

And PS. if you want even more info, you can head over to our latest blog post 'Decoding Deodorant Strengths'.
